Go with the flow.

19:04.177 --> 19:05.610
Dad, what the hell?!

19:05.612 --> 19:07.645
(metal screeching)

19:07.647 --> 19:10.348
I'm doing it, Hayley!
It feels amazing!

19:10.350 --> 19:12.683
What are you doing?!
I'm improvising!

19:12.685 --> 19:14.652
Our plan was to beat Bullock.

19:14.654 --> 19:17.421
But if we keep him from
competing, he'll still lose.

19:17.423 --> 19:20.191
Ooooh!
Ahhh!

19:20.193 --> 19:22.326
Oh, my God,
you're right.

19:22.328 --> 19:24.462
A-and you just came up
with that?

19:24.464 --> 19:26.531
Yes!
Like improv!

19:26.533 --> 19:29.033
Whose line is it, anyway?!

19:29.035 --> 19:31.702
BULLOCK: What a light show!

19:31.704 --> 19:33.671
Oh, Stan's
having an accident.

19:33.673 --> 19:35.139
Look at me go!

19:35.141 --> 19:36.607
Look at you go!

19:36.609 --> 19:38.309
That's living without a plan.

19:38.311 --> 19:41.479
It's so freeing -- I can see why
you want to live this way.

19:41.481 --> 19:44.182
I'm sorry I was trying to
change you, baby girl.

19:44.184 --> 19:46.951
(thudding)

19:46.953 --> 19:49.220
(grinding)

19:49.222 --> 19:51.222
You pushed him right to
the club!

19:51.224 --> 19:52.857
(struggles)
It's stuck!

19:52.859 --> 19:55.026
If he deejays,
I'm as good as dead.

19:55.028 --> 19:58.896
Thank God my pipe didn't break.

19:58.898 --> 20:02.133
(inhales)

20:02.135 --> 20:04.869
(tires screech)

20:04.871 --> 20:07.572
(roars)

20:07.574 --> 20:09.273
(gasps)
The dragon!

20:11.811 --> 20:13.077
Get up, you fool!

20:13.079 --> 20:14.812
But the turin's played
lying down.

20:14.814 --> 20:17.381
Of course it is.

20:17.383 --> 20:19.150
(beautiful music plays)

20:19.152 --> 20:20.918
That music.

20:20.920 --> 20:24.322
It's so soothing.

20:24.324 --> 20:28.092
(music continues)

20:31.764 --> 20:33.364
Oh, baby.

20:33.366 --> 20:35.099
You are a dragon soother.

20:35.101 --> 20:37.034
I was wrong
about you, Jeff.

20:37.036 --> 20:40.571
You're no bum.
You're a street musician.

20:40.573 --> 20:42.607
Entertainer of bums.

20:42.609 --> 20:46.277
(crying)

20:46.279 --> 20:48.079
Dad, go win this thing.

20:48.081 --> 20:50.715
But -- but I don't have to.

20:50.717 --> 20:53.351
And I don't want to.

20:53.353 --> 20:56.120
Well, that just leaves
one loose end.

20:56.122 --> 20:59.724
This is a turin, Wayne.

